1
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,880
Who are you? Why are you here?

2
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,960
You have no shame.

3
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:43,120
Look at yourself.

4
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,000
You don't look like a Bai at all.

5
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,080
Look at this place.

6
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:48,320
Do you belong here?

7
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:53,479
You don't even know who your parents are.

8
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:55,600
How do you have the nerve to stand here?

9
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:57,600
You are a disgrace to the Bai family.

10
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,600
How can you shamelessly stay in

11
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,800
our Bai family?

12
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,680
You are so pitiful.

13
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,520
You are so pitiful.

14
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,039
What a disgrace.

15
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:13,520
Why are you staying here?

16
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:17,040
Bastard. Disgusting bastard.

17
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,040
Unwanted bastard.

18
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,760
The Bai family doesn't want a bastard like you.

19
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:20,280
You bastard.

20
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,560
No one wants a bastard.

21
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:33,280
Bastard. Bastard.

22
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,400
Chuyi, are you okay?

23
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:49,079
Chuyi.

24
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:59,760
She's always been healthy.

25
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,320
Why is she so weak these past two days?

26
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:05,120
Adai, is someone bullying her at the academy?

27
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:08,000
But Chuyi told me before,

28
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,800
the problems at the academy were resolved.

29
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,500
Then what's wrong with Chuyi?

30
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,760
Chuyi, don't be afraid. It's me.

31
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,200
Chuyi, tell me.

32
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,200
What happened?

33
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,200
Don't come over!

34
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:29,560
Why is she suddenly so afraid of you?

35
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:31,320
Did you beat her secretly?

36
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:34,840
Say that again, and I'll beat you right now.

37
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,290
Sister-in-law.

38
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:42,160
Are you really my brother and sister-in-law?

39
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,520
What do you mean, real or fake?

40
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,480
I'm your brother.

41
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,440
The real deal.

42
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:50,160
But I'm no longer your Chuyi.

43
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,040
Oh, you child.

44
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:53,100
What nonsense are you talking about?

45
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:55,920
I've changed. I've become a stranger.

46
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,600
I'm not myself anymore.

47
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,880
Can I still be Bai Chuyi?

48
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,600
You are Bai Chuyi.

49
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,960
No matter what happens,

50
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,120
you are my sister.

51
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,480
If anyone dares say otherwise,

52
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,080
I'll break their legs.

53
00:04:07,200 --> 00:04:10,800
Chuyi, family bond is more important than blood.

54
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:14,440
Chuyi, did someone talk nonsense to you?

55
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,920
No.

56
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,720
I just had a nightmare.

57
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,040
It felt so real.

58
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:22,540
I was afraid of turning into something else.

59
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,420
And you wouldn't want me anymore.

60
00:04:25,840 --> 00:04:27,240
It was just a dream.

61
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,920
Dreams are fake.

62
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:31,480
Don't trust what you see with your eyes.

63
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,920
Feel with your heart.

64
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,680
Chuyi, as long as you come back home,

65
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,880
and acknowledge me as your big brother,

66
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,800
we will be together forever.

67
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,280
We won't leave you behind.

68
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,520
Huanghuacai.

69
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,840
I'm happy today.

70
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:57,720
Will anyone dance with me?

71
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:25,480
Huanghuacai, why are you here?

72
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:32,200
You dreamt of me, so here I am.

73
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,760
Let's go.

74
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:54,520
Huanghuacai, since when can you dance?

75
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:58,000
I learned it for you, of course.

76
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,210
Husband, you've been busy lately.

77
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:09,010
And often can't sleep at night.

78
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:12,720
Since when do you care about me so much?

79
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:15,520
If it weren't for me,

80
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,720
you wouldn't be this exhausted.

81
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:24,160
It is my duty to solve your problems, My Lady.

82
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:35,840
Husband, no matter what happens,

83
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,810
I'll always be by your side.

84
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:41,560
You sound like a steward.

85
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,580
I don't want to manage you.

86
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,320
Huanghuacai.

87
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,960
You're much better behaved in dreams.

88
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,920
Then do you like this?

89
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:11,040
I like you no matter what.

90
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,600
What if I said,

91
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:15,440
you could only love one person in this life?

92
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,880
Would you agree?

93
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:20,440
You never ask things like that.

94
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,480
I'll take your silence as a yes.

95
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:27,240
You never ask about such things.

96
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:30,280
I don't ask because I'm reserved.

97
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,480
But this is a dream.

98
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:35,280
I can do whatever I want.

99
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:40,200
You're so naughty.

100
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,159
You're so cold, Husband.

101
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,840
Let me warm you up.

102
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,600
But my heart is warm.

103
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:54,920
It's full of you.

104
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:58,040
This is a dream.

105
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,960
You can do whatever you want.

106
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,280
It's about time.

107
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,920
Huanghuacai.

108
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,679
What took you so long?
